  "description": "<p>Job Highlight<br>\n<br>\n5 Days Work Week, Monday to Friday 8am to 5.30pm<br>\nImmediate Hiring or within short notice<br>\nLocation: 22 Jurong Port Road Tower B #04-02<br>\nAttractive company benefit<br>\nBasic Salary: $1800 to $2800 (Salary is depending on experience)<br>\nRESPONSIBILITIES<br>\n<br>\nStock reconciliation<br>\nMonthly sales report<br>\nMonthly Commission report<br>\nInvoicing and delivery coordination<br>\nHandle Invoicing / Accounts Payable / Accounts Receivables<br>\nUndertake any other duties in relation to the job scope as assigned by your superior from time to time<br>\nREQUIREMENTS<br>\n<br>\nO” level and above, Diploma of accounting<br>\nMinimum 1 years of working experience in the related field<br>\nProficient in MYOB, Microsoft Excel<br>\nBasic Accounting knowledge<br>\n<br>\nWe regret that only suitable candidate will be notified.</p>",
